page.title: 15HOUSING AROUND WEELEY
page.content: In Weeley, there are many styles of houses and buildings. In the{estate} areas (where the majority of the inhabitants are elderly people){ {bungalows}are most frequent. Whereas the houses outside the town are larger, and older houses. There is one house just outside{ {Weeley}called{Kenilworth}which is inhabited by a very wealthy man. This house is very large and unlike the majority of houses around Weeley, fairly old. Also there are some houses which are very unusually built. In the actual town the majority of houses are semi-detatched.
